59
00:12:33,460 --> 00:12:34,620
What's this place?

60
00:12:35,900 --> 00:12:36,900
What is this place for?

61
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:39,220
As you can see,

62
00:12:39,860 --> 00:12:40,780
