64
00:12:46,820 --> 00:12:48,260
Isn't this place a library?

65
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:51,260
How can there be such a place in it?

66
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:54,740
We don't worship gods or Buddhas here.

67
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:56,780
Instead, we pay homage to the dead.

68
00:12:57,540 --> 00:12:58,860
The dead in Zhao Yun Temple.

69
00:12:59,420 --> 00:13:00,220
The dead?

70
00:13:00,420 --> 00:13:00,900
Yes.

71
00:13:01,460 --> 00:13:02,500
Two hundred years ago,

72
00:13:02,540 --> 00:13:04,020
