73
00:13:04,820 --> 00:13:06,180
Its name was also Zhao Yun.

74
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:08,340
It was a tumultuous period at that time.

75
00:13:08,700 --> 00:13:09,980
Besides Taoists,

76
00:13:10,260 --> 00:13:12,380
