77
00:13:12,580 --> 00:13:13,420
and scholars here.

78
00:13:14,420 --> 00:13:15,380
One night,

79
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:17,300
a group of roving bandits
attacked the temple.

80
00:13:17,740 --> 00:13:20,060
In order to get a treasure
that might not exist,

81
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:22,780
they killed all the Taoists,

82
00:13:22,780 --> 00:13:23,900
commoners,

83
00:13:23,900 --> 00:13:25,060
and scholars here.

84
00:13:27,780 --> 00:13:30,420
That was really a bloody massacre.

85
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:34,300
Later on,

86
00:13:34,700 --> 00:13:37,100
this place became
a dilapidated and haunted abode.

87
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:38,500
It had been deserted for a hundred years.

88
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:40,020
Later,

89
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:41,700
about 40 years ago,

90
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:43,180
the world became peaceful.

91
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:46,420
Our teacher came here by chance.

92
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,420
He renovated this place

93
00:13:49,580 --> 00:13:51,540
