97
00:14:03,180 --> 00:14:04,740
[Mr. Zhou Li's Memorial Tablet]

98
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:06,820
Our teacher also asked us

99
00:14:06,900 --> 00:14:08,300
to bring some offerings here

100
