101
00:14:10,900 --> 00:14:12,380
or when it was a festival.

102
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:14,260
Although we don't perform
a religious rite,

103
00:14:14,260 --> 00:14:15,580
we believe

104
00:14:15,940 --> 00:14:17,020
these offerings

105
00:14:17,340 --> 00:14:18,940
can soothe the souls of the dead.

106
00:14:21,220 --> 00:14:22,220
I see.

107
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:25,420
Miss Cao,

108
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:29,980
why are you here?

109
00:14:31,260 --> 00:14:32,180
Does Mr. Cui

110
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:36,100
know

111
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:39,300
the death of Zhou Li?

112
00:14:45,140 --> 00:14:46,020
When our teacher's retreat

113
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:47,860
