143
00:16:10,940 --> 00:16:12,140
I don't believe in such things.

144
00:16:13,060 --> 00:16:14,380
At first, I didn't believe
in these things, either.

145
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:16,580
But our teacher believes in them.

146
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:19,660
He showed me

147
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:22,620
that our understanding of the world

148
00:16:22,860 --> 00:16:23,820
may be only

149
00:16:24,100 --> 00:16:26,060
one ten-thousandth
of the truth of the world.

150
00:16:26,660 --> 00:16:30,340
One day, there will be an explanation

151
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:31,900
for those unknown things

152
00:16:32,460 --> 00:16:33,860
like ghosts, gods, and Buddhas.

153
00:16:34,780 --> 00:16:35,420
Now we can only

154
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:38,660
understand it simply as a magnetic field.

155
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:41,020
As the weather has changed,

156
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:42,460
Yin Qi in this place is very heavy.

157
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:44,100
Plus the Magistrate

158
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:45,420
was very weak.

159
00:16:45,780 --> 00:16:48,500
So his magnetic field might
have been disturbed,

160
00:16:49,060 --> 00:16:50,580
