165
00:16:57,780 --> 00:16:59,460
We can also call them

166
00:17:00,540 --> 00:17:01,420
obsessions.

167
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:03,340
An obsession

168
00:17:03,900 --> 00:17:04,660
may concern

169
00:17:05,460 --> 00:17:06,660
something happened long ago

170
00:17:07,340 --> 00:17:08,580
or

171
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:10,580
a deceased person.

172
