223
00:21:47,980 --> 00:21:48,540
That's right.

224
00:21:49,220 --> 00:21:50,620
Each footprint was about this big.

225
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:52,340
Each one was very deep.

226
00:21:53,020 --> 00:21:54,380
The man seemed to be very heavy.

227
00:21:55,220 --> 00:21:56,860
The incense that was given to Mr. Cui

228
00:21:57,140 --> 00:21:58,620
