237
00:22:23,460 --> 00:22:24,220
Yeah.

238
00:22:27,420 --> 00:22:28,700
What I want to say is

239
00:22:29,660 --> 00:22:32,700
that there are too many mysteries
we haven't solved.

240
00:22:34,820 --> 00:22:35,820
Possessed by the dead,

241
00:22:36,420 --> 00:22:39,100
Zhou Li jumped down and died.

242
