246
00:22:52,700 --> 00:22:54,340
I saw

247
00:22:55,180 --> 00:22:56,740
that child in white again.

248
00:22:57,620 --> 00:22:58,340
Where did you see him?

249
00:23:10,340 --> 00:23:12,900
Do you know there will be
a solar eclipse this month?

250
00:23:13,540 --> 00:23:15,260
On such dismal days,

251
00:23:15,900 --> 00:23:17,220
the dead here

252
00:23:17,580 --> 00:23:19,220
are always restless.

253
00:23:20,780 --> 00:23:22,300
As the weather has changed,

254
00:23:22,420 --> 00:23:24,060
Yin Qi in this place is very heavy.

255
00:23:24,500 --> 00:23:26,700
