256
00:23:26,860 --> 00:23:29,180
So his magnetic field might
have been disturbed,

257
00:23:29,180 --> 00:23:30,660
causing the instability of his mind.

258
00:23:32,340 --> 00:23:33,980
Ever since I came here,

259
00:23:34,340 --> 00:23:36,100
I've been having a strange feeling.

260
00:23:36,860 --> 00:23:39,180
It seems a pair of eyes are watching me.

261
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:40,740
The solar eclipse is coming.

262
00:23:40,860 --> 00:23:43,020
Let's not offend the dead.

263
00:23:43,820 --> 00:23:46,660
No, that's not the dead.

264
00:23:47,340 --> 00:23:49,460
I know what I saw.

265
00:23:52,020 --> 00:23:52,780
Maybe

266
00:23:53,420 --> 00:23:55,260
