267
00:23:55,780 --> 00:23:57,100
Or maybe you just saw

268
00:23:57,260 --> 00:23:58,940
your own obsession.

269
00:24:06,060 --> 00:24:08,460
The dead won't disturb the living.

270
00:24:10,180 --> 00:24:12,340
Maybe you haven't forgotten him.

271
00:24:13,140 --> 00:24:15,180
But I won't let him

272
00:24:15,900 --> 00:24:17,500
