280
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:57,020
Thank you.

281
00:24:58,700 --> 00:24:59,740
We also want

282
00:24:59,860 --> 00:25:01,180
to leave the library as soon as possible.

283
00:25:02,100 --> 00:25:02,820
Okay.

284
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:05,540
Well,

285
00:25:06,580 --> 00:25:07,620
when it stops snowing,

286
00:25:07,860 --> 00:25:09,940
I'll ask someone to send you
down the mountain at once.

287
00:25:10,980 --> 00:25:11,980
Thank you.

288
00:25:12,660 --> 00:25:13,980
Give it to the Magistrate now.

289
00:25:14,620 --> 00:25:15,220
Goodbye.

290
00:25:30,700 --> 00:25:31,940
The medicine Mr. Li has sent here.

